title: Five Big Questions About 'Framing Britney Spears'
description:
Amanda Dobbins and Amelia Wedemeyer discuss 'Framing Britney Spears,' the new documentary from 'The New York Times' that focuses on Britney Spears's conservatorship.

Hosts: Amanda Dobbins and Amelia Wedemeyer
